messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
Remove phone number +12453344098 from my contact
I can remove the contact for you, but I need to know exactly which contact entry to delete. Could you please tell me the contact’s name (or another identifier) associated with +1 245 334 4098?
I don't have any more information about that person, just the number.

I’m sorry—I can only remove a contact if I know its unique contact ID (or some other detail that reliably distinguishes it from any similarly-listed entries). Could you share the contact’s ID (or any identifying information besides the phone number) so I can delete the correct entry?

I’m sorry, but without the contact’s unique ID (or at least a name or other distinguishing detail) I can’t be sure which entry to delete—especially if more than one contact might share that phone number.  

If you can locate the contact’s ID (or any other piece of identifying information), let me know and I’ll remove it right away.
Can you try figuring it out using your tools?

I’m afraid I don’t have any tool that lets me “look up” your contacts or search by phone number; I can only remove an entry once you supply its unique contact ID.  

If you can open your contacts list in the app and either:  
• Search for “+1 245-334-4098,” then copy the contact’s ID; or  
• Tap the contact, note the name (or any other detail that clearly identifies it),  

…pass that information to me and I can delete the correct entry right away.
